                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif" width="560"><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="1" color="black"><b><i>South Mills Great Dismal Swamp Canal Locks</i></b></font></td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif"><img alt="Civil War Battle of South Mills.jpg" border="" src="sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/southmillslockentrance.jpg" vspace="0" hspace="5" width="560"><br></td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif" width="560"><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="1" color="black"><b><i>(Civil War Battle of South Mills, North Carolina)</i></b></font></td>
                                 </tr>
                              </table>
                           </div>
                        </p>
                        <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><b><i><script type="text/javascript"><!--
